function AboutMe() { return (

about me

Musician + Artist + Designer + Programmer + Writer

BS, Digital Media from University of Houston

DJ, KTRU 96.1

Founder, Forum Cache® + reserve® jazz publication.

Art has my life and music has my heart. Exploring both through design, technology (digital and analog), and language has been my focus since the early 2010s. I believe that the real work lies in solving problems that impede on the livelihood of people all over the world. I'm interested in iterating/reiterating new systems for sustainable living, developing independent, self-sufficient black cultural institutions, and funding/contributing to decolonization projects.

) } export default AboutMe;
